</m:mfrac>
</m:mtd>
</m:mtr>
</m:mtable>
</m:math>
</para>
<para id="element-36">
This is important from the perspective that external force can be expressed in terms of acceleration :
</para>
<para id="element-37">
<m:math display="block">
